    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really great shape and has been super reliable\u2014perfect for someone looking for a solid, well-cared-for ride that's ready for its next adventure. It drives like a dream and is ready to hit the road today! Let me know if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
