    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. The engine retains excellent compression, breathing through factory individual throttle bodies and delivering a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and the M Variable Differential Lock. This chassis has been proactively maintained with a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, addressing the primary concerns for this platform. Recent service includes a precise valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system refresh. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with high-performance use, the mechanical vitals and suspension kinematics remain tight, making this an ideal candidate for the spirited driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
