    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a well-maintained 2018 Executive Sedan that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior retains a lustrous factory finish, though close inspection reveals minor road peppering on the front fascia and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of premium materials; the leather upholstery is supple and intact, showing only light character creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the navigation system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this vehicle has been fastidiously cared for with a documented service history, ensuring the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly. The tires have significant tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident feedback. This is a reliable, attractive vehicle that has been kept in a smoke-free, pet-free environment and is fully prepared for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
