      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been so reliable and is still in really great shape! I\u2019ve taken wonderful care of it, so it\u2019s ready for many more adventures with you. It runs smoothly and looks fantastic inside and out. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
